                                                     <div class="fusion-panel panel-default fusion-faq-post ">
                                                        <span class="entry-title rich-snippet-hidden">
                                                            Dushtho Paribar Unnayan Sangstha signed contract with DataSoft                                                        </span>
                                                        <div class="panel-heading">
                                                            <h4 class="panel-title toggle">
                                                                <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordian-1" data-target="#collapse-1-501" href="#collapse-1-501">
                                                                    <div class="fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper">
                                                                        <i class="fa fa-newspaper-o"></i>
                                                                    </div>
                                                                    <div class="fusion-toggle-heading">Dushtho Paribar Unnayan Sangstha signed contract with DataSoft</div>
                                                                </a>
                                                            </h4>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div id="collapse-1-501" class="panel-collapse collapse" style="height: auto; text-align: justify;">
                                                            <div class="panel-body toggle-content post-content"><p><strong>April 1, 2018</strong></p>
                                                                <p>
                                                                    <img class="alignnone wp-image-12450 size-full" src="https://microfin360.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/501.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="600" srcset="https://microfin360.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/501-200x150.jpg 200w, https://microfin360.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/501-300x225.jpg 300w, https://microfin360.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/501-400x300.jpg 400w, https://microfin360.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/501-600x450.jpg 600w, https://microfin360.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/501-768x576.jpg 768w, https://microfin360.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/501.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
                                                                <p>“DataSoft Systems Bangladesh Limited” and “Dushtho Paribar Unnayan Sangstha”, have signed a contract today to work jointly in Microcredit Branch Automation process. MicroFin360 is our web-based, dash-board driven Micro-Finance Management software specially developed for the Microfinance Institutes to automate their work-flow. The solution comes with an immense capability of synchronizing real time data, management level monitoring and centralized financial report consolidation. By means of adopting the solution, every aspect of microfinance business would readily be performed with secured transactional data entry which needs less effort and human touch. The solution also runs in compliance with Regulatory Authorities, Patrons, Partners, Donors and Funding Organizations. Microfinance organizations can avail this solution integrated with Management Information System (MIS), Financial Information System (FIS) and Human Resource (HR) modules.
	<br>
Throughout the last decade of MicroFin360’s successful journey it has already facilitated hundreds of Microfinance Institutions upon ensuring them a successful automation both from home and abroad. Till date DataSoft has signed One Hundred and Seventeen (117) MFI’s and has covered 4,877 of their branches so far.</p>
